Name: Average time from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to Manuscript Export Succeeded

Name: Total time from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Average time between Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation and SW-Awaiting AE Assignment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Minimum time from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to Plagiarism Originality Report Completed
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Time until SW-Reviewer Agreed after Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Average time to reach SW-Awaiting EIC Decision after Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Average time for Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to lead to a SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit decision
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': "activity == 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'", 'end': "activity == 'SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit'", 'aggregation': 'average'}

Name: Elapsed time between Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation and SW-Reviewer No Response
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Reviewer No Response'

Name: Time from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to SW-EIC Major Revision
